までこれ攻撃することになる。これが、憲法が禁止した、放棄した戦争でなくて何なのか…", "…止した、放棄した戦争でなくて何なのかと。相手国から見れば、これは先制攻撃にほかなりません。報復を呼びます。我が国に戦火を呼び込むことになりま…", "…ことになります。私は、安保法制、戦争法の危険性がいよいよ、この敵基地攻撃の問題も含めてですね、いよいよこの危険性が明らかになったと思います。…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/314", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/316", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/318", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/320", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/322", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/324", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/326", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/328", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/330", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/332", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/335", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/337", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/339", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/341", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/344", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/346", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/348", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/350", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/354", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/360", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531/362", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01920220531